Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:57.81,Main,Se,0,0,0,,Aká sila!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:01.79,Main,F,0,0,0,,Naozaj sa snaží zničiť svet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.05,Main,Gm,0,0,0,,To je taká zábava!
